trans-unit.source: Represents a language tag for use in XAML markup.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en språkkode for bruk i XAML markup.

trans-unit.source: The language tag may or may not have a registered <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> present on the system where the XAML is interpreted.
trans-unit.target: Språk-ID kan eller kan ikke ha en registrert <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>på systemet der XAML tolkes.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: This class is useful for dealing with values represented using `xml:lang` in XML.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen er nyttig for håndtering av verdiene som er representert ved hjelp av `xml:lang` i XML.

trans-unit.source: Language tags can be specified in two-character form or in a hyphenated language-locale form.
trans-unit.target: Språket koder kan angis i to tegn eller i et skjema med bindestrek språk.

trans-unit.source: See [RFC 3066](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=132454).
trans-unit.target: Se [RFC 3066](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=132454).

trans-unit.source: Note that the XML specification allows the empty string for `xml:lang`, although that is not permitted by RFC 3066; therefore, the XmlLanguage type permits "" (empty attribute string).
trans-unit.target: Legg merke til at XML-spesifikasjon tillater en tom streng for `xml:lang`, selv om som ikke er tillatt av RFC 3066; derfor XmlLanguage typen tillater "" (tom attributtet streng).

trans-unit.source: A default-constructed XmlLanguage behaves as if constructed with "" (empty string).
trans-unit.target: En standard konstruert XmlLanguage fungere som om konstruert med "" (tom streng).

trans-unit.source: ## XAML Attribute Usage ``` - or - ``` ## XAML Values *prefix* Language prefix, using the ISO 639-1 language prefix values.
trans-unit.target: ## XAML Attributtbruk ``` - or - ``` ## XAML verdier *prefikset* språket prefiks, ved hjelp av ISO 639-1 språket prefikset verdiene.

trans-unit.source: For example "en", or "zh".
trans-unit.target: For eksempel "no" eller "zh".

trans-unit.source: Uppercase values are accepted and converted to lowercase.
trans-unit.target: Store verdier er godkjent og konvertert til små bokstaver.

trans-unit.source: This may also be an empty attribute, "".
trans-unit.target: Dette kan også være en tom attributtet "".

trans-unit.source: *subcode* If provided, must be preceded by a single hyphen.
trans-unit.target: *Delkode* hvis angitt, må komme etter en enkelt bindestrek.

trans-unit.source: Then, a subcode as defined by RFC 3066.
trans-unit.target: Deretter en delkode som er definert av RFC 3066.

trans-unit.source: The most typical usage, and the one which is most likely to properly map to a <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>, is a country or regional designation such as "-us" or "-hk".
trans-unit.target: Mest vanlig bruk, og det som er mest sannsynlig vil er riktig tilordnet en <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>, er et land eller regionale angivelsen for eksempel "-oss" eller "-hk".</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: Uppercase values are accepted and converted to lowercase.
trans-unit.target: Store verdier er godkjent og konvertert til små bokstaver.

trans-unit.source: Gets a static <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"></xref> instance as would be created by <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetLanguage*> with the language tag as an empty attribute string.
trans-unit.target: Henter en statisk <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"> </xref> serverforekomsten som er laget ved <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetLanguage*>med koden språket som en tom attributtet-streng.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetLanguage*>

trans-unit.source: This value is in effect the <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage> corresponding to <xref:System.String.Empty?displayProperty=fullName>, whose <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetEquivalentCulture%2A> result is <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Denne verdien er i bruk av <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage>tilsvarende til <xref:System.String.Empty?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetEquivalentCulture%2A>resultatet er <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetEquivalentCulture%2A> </xref:System.String.Empty?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage>

trans-unit.source: The empty language tag version of <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"></xref>, for use in comparison operations.
trans-unit.target: En tom koden språkversjon av <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"> </xref>, for bruk i sammenligningsoperasjoner.

trans-unit.source: Returns the appropriate equivalent <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> for this <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"></xref>, if and only if such a <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> is registered for the <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.IetfLanguageTag*> value of this <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"></xref>
trans-unit.target: Returnerer den riktige tilsvarende <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>for denne <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"> </xref>, hvis og bare hvis slike en <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>er registrert for den <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.IetfLanguageTag*>verdien for dette <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"> </xref> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.IetfLanguageTag*> </xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> </xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: If no equivalent <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> can be produced, this method raises an exception.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen tilsvarende <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>kan være angitt, denne metoden viser et unntak.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: If you do not wish to handle exceptions, call <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetSpecificCulture%2A> instead.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke vil behandle unntak, kaller <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetSpecificCulture%2A>i stedet.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetSpecificCulture%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> that can be used for localization-globalization API calls that take that type as an argument.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>som kan brukes for lokalisering globalisering API-kall som tar denne typen som argument.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: No registered <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> for the provided <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"></xref> exists, as determined by a call to <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.GetCultureInfoByIetfLanguageTag*>.
trans-unit.target: Ingen registrert <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>for den angitte <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"> </xref> finnes, i henhold til et kall til <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.GetCultureInfoByIetfLanguageTag*>.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.GetCultureInfoByIetfLanguageTag*> </xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"></xref> instance, based on a string representing the language per RFC 3066.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"> </xref> forekomsten, basert på en streng som representerer språket per RFC 3066.

trans-unit.source: This method is effectively the constructor.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden er effektivt konstruktøren.

trans-unit.source: The language string may be empty, or else must conform to [RFC 3066](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=132454) rules: - The first subtag must consist of only [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ascii](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ascii-md.md)] letters.
trans-unit.target: Språk-streng kan være tom, ellers må samsvare med [RFC 3066](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=132454) regler:-første subtag må bestå av bare [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ascii](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ascii-md.md)] bokstaver.

trans-unit.source: - Additional subtags must consist [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ascii](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ascii-md.md)] letters or numerals.
trans-unit.target: -Flere subtags må bestå [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ascii](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ascii-md.md)] tall.

trans-unit.source: - Subtags are separated by a single hyphen character.
trans-unit.target: -Subtags atskilt med et enkelt bindestrek tegn.

trans-unit.source: - Every subtag must be 1 to 8 characters long.
trans-unit.target: -Hver subtag må være 1 til 8 tegn.

trans-unit.source: - No leading or trailing hyphens are permitted.
trans-unit.target: -Uten innledende eller avsluttende bindestreker er tillatt.

trans-unit.source: An RFC 3066 language string, or empty string.
trans-unit.target: En RFC 3066 språket streng, eller en tom streng.

trans-unit.source: A new <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"></xref> with the provided string as its <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.IetfLanguageTag*> value.
trans-unit.target: En ny <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"> </xref> med den angitte strengen som den <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.IetfLanguageTag*>verdi.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.IetfLanguageTag*>

trans-unit.source: ietfLanguageTag parameter cannot be null.
trans-unit.target: ietfLanguageTagparameteren kan ikke være null.

trans-unit.source: ietfLanguageTag parameter was non-empty, but did not conform to the syntax specified in RFC 3066.
trans-unit.target: ietfLanguageTagparameteren ble ikke er tom, men samsvarer ikke med kravene syntaksen angitt i RFC 3066.

trans-unit.source: See Remarks.
trans-unit.target: Se kommentarer.

trans-unit.source: Returns the most-closely-related non-neutral <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> for this <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer det nært relaterte ikke nøytralt <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>for denne <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"> </xref>.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: If this <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage> is equal to <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.Empty%2A?displayProperty=fullName> then this method will return <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis dette <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage>er lik <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.Empty%2A?displayProperty=fullName>deretter denne metoden tilbakestiller <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.Empty%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage>

trans-unit.source: This method finds the registered <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> matching the longest-possible prefix of this <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage>.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden finner den registrerte <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>samsvarende lengste mulig prefikset for <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage>.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage> </xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: If that registered <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> is neutral (<xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.IsNeutralCulture%2A> is `true`), then this method relies on a call to <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.CreateSpecificCulture%2A> to map from a neutral <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> to a specific one.
trans-unit.target: Hvis som er registrert <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>er nøytral (<xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.IsNeutralCulture%2A> er `true`), og denne metoden, avhengig av et kall til <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.CreateSpecificCulture%2A>skal tilordnes fra en nøytral <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>til et bestemt.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> </xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.CreateSpecificCulture%2A> </xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.IsNeutralCulture%2A> </xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> that can be used for localization-globalization [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_api](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-api-md.md)] calls that take that type as an argument.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>som kan brukes for lokalisering globalisering [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_api](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-api-md.md)] anrop som tar denne typen som argument.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: No related non-neutral <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> is registered for the current <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"></xref> <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.IetfLanguageTag*>.
trans-unit.target: Ingen relaterte ikke nøytral <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>er registrert for gjeldende <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"> </xref> <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.IetfLanguageTag*>.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.IetfLanguageTag*> </xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: Gets the string representation of the language tag.
trans-unit.target: Henter strengrepresentasjon av koden språk.

trans-unit.source: This property may return a normalized version of the originally-specified string as provided to <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetLanguage%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan returnere en normalisert versjon av strengen som opprinnelig ble angitt som sendes til <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetLanguage%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetLanguage%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property may also return <xref:System.String.Empty> if an empty string was provided to <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetLanguage%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan også returnere <xref:System.String.Empty>Hvis en tom streng ble oppgitt til <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetLanguage%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage.GetLanguage%2A> </xref:System.String.Empty>
